title: Political career of Donald Trump
added: [[Donald Trump]] has been a presidential candidate three times, in [[Donald Trump presidential campaign, 2000|2000]], [[2016 Donald Trump presidential campaign|2016]], and [[2020 Donald Trump presidential campaign|2020]]. His second presidential campaign in 2016 was successful; he was [[2016 United States presidential election|elected]] [[List of presidents of the United States#Presidents|45th]] [[president of the United States]] on November 8, 2016 and [[Inauguration of Donald Trump|inaugurated on January 20, 2017]]. He sought reelection in the [[2020 United States presidential election]], but lost to [[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]] nominee [[Joe Biden]].
